AND I HAD SEX,

05:07.291 --> 05:09.250
WE CREATED
SOME SORT OF...

05:09.250 --> 05:11.000
COSMIC IMBALANCE, OK?

05:11.000 --> 05:12.959
LIKE, A KARMIC
DISTURBANCE,
IF YOU WILL,

05:12.959 --> 05:13.875
AND WHAT THIS MEANS IS

05:13.875 --> 05:16.333
THAT BAD ENERGY
IS SEEKING US OUT.

05:16.333 --> 05:19.750
OK? IT'S HERE,
AND IT'S HOVERING.

05:21.417 --> 05:22.458
HMM.

05:22.458 --> 05:23.834
WELL, I DON'T KNOW HOW
TO TELL YOU THIS,

05:23.834 --> 05:25.583
BUT THOSE GUYS
IN GHOSTBUSTERS,

05:25.583 --> 05:27.083
THEY'RE NOT REAL SCIENTISTS.

05:27.083 --> 05:28.667
