BUT NEVER KEPT,

07:50.125 --> 07:51.166
DOOMED LOVE
AT ITS FINEST.

07:51.166 --> 07:53.125
IT'S VERY HENRY JAMES,
SLASH, EDITH WHARTON.

07:53.125 --> 07:54.375
VERY LILY BART.

07:54.375 --> 07:56.667
IN FACT, ANYONE
EVER COMPARE YOU

07:56.667 --> 07:58.041
