08:05.750 --> 08:07.291
MAYBE--MAYBE, UH, UH,
FANNY PRICE PERHAPS

08:07.291 --> 08:09.500
OR--OR JANE EYRE MAYBE.

08:09.500 --> 08:10.834
IN ANY CASE,
THAT'S WHO YOU ARE.

08:10.834 --> 08:11.834
YOU'RE THE GIRL

08:11.834 --> 08:13.542
IN THE 19th CENTURY NOVEL

08:13.542 --> 08:15.291
WHO WOULD PERVERSELY
REFUSE TO MARRY FOR MONEY

08:15.291 --> 08:17.708
