PROMISE YOU THAT.

08:33.125 --> 08:35.207
THEN I'M AFRAID WE'RE
AT AN IMPASSE HERE.

08:38.375 --> 08:39.000
SO...

08:39.000 --> 08:41.500
THAT'S IT?

