08:52.166 --> 08:54.083
BEST ENDING
IN ALL OF LITERATURE,

08:54.083 --> 08:55.375
AND DON'T SAY ULYSSES

08:55.375 --> 08:57.208
BECAUSE EVERYBODY
SAYS ULYSSES.

08:57.208 --> 08:58.333
YOU CAN'T BE SERIOUS.

08:58.333 --> 09:00.792
I THINK WE BOTH KNOW
WHAT HAPPENED FRIDAY NIGHT.

09:02.166 --> 09:04.208
