HAVING SEX.

10:54.375 --> 10:56.750
FINALLY, SOMEONE
WHO AGREES WITH ME,

10:56.750 --> 10:58.208
SO LOOK, COULD YOU
JUST GO UP THERE

10:58.208 --> 11:00.125
