I'M GONNA HANG.

35:50.625 --> 35:52.750
OK, COOL. I'LL SEE YOU
AROUND, MAN.
OK.

35:58.500 --> 35:58.917
TAKE CARE, AUDREY.

35:58.917 --> 36:02.291
OH, MAN.

36:02.291 --> 36:04.583
IT'S BEEN
THOROUGHLY, UH...

36:04.583 --> 36:06.417
SLANTED AND ENCHANTED.

36:06.417 --> 36:08.708
