SEE YA.

36:19.000 --> 36:21.333
SO, YOUR--
YOUR BOYFRIEND.

36:21.333 --> 36:24.708
I MEAN, IT MUST HAVE BEEN
LOVE AT FIRST SIGHT.

36:24.708 --> 36:26.834
