YOUR RELATIONSHIP.

36:48.250 --> 36:50.166
I MEAN, IT'S JUST...

36:50.166 --> 36:51.291
I BELIEVE
IN THE CONNECTION.

36:51.291 --> 36:53.375
YOU KNOW,
THAT GUT REACTION

36:53.375 --> 36:57.625
