THIS STRANGER...

36:57.625 --> 37:01.834
IS MEANT TO BE
A PART OF MY LIFE,"
AND I DON'T KNOW.

37:01.834 --> 37:03.875
I--I GUESS I JUST FELT
THAT FOR YOU TONIGHT.

37:03.875 --> 37:07.041
YEAH, WELL, THAT'S
A REALLY EASY THING

37:07.041 --> 37:09.417
FOR YOU TO SAY,
ISN'T IT?

37:09.417 --> 37:10.917
SOME
ROCK AND ROLL GUY

37:10.917 --> 37:14.917
