TO REMEMBER US BY.

37:30.708 --> 37:32.667
[CHUCKLES]
THANKS.

37:32.667 --> 37:34.083
DON'T MENTION IT.

37:36.750 --> 37:37.750
BYE.

37:37.750 --> 37:40.083
BYE.

37:41.542 --> 37:46.458
YOU KNOW, THIS WAS SO
NOT THE NIGHT I EXPECTED.

37:46.458 --> 37:47.834
YEAH, I KNOW.
SORRY I TOOK
THE SINGLE ONE.

37:47.834 --> 37:50.041
NAH, IT HAPPENS.

37:50.041 --> 37:51.333
YOU KNOW, MAYBE IT'S GOD'S
WAY OF TELLING ME

37:51.333 --> 37:53.375
