JUST GO TO HIM.

38:07.250 --> 38:09.375
OK.

38:09.375 --> 38:10.834
BYE.
BYE, SWEETIE.

38:25.417 --> 38:26.417
SHE NEED A RIDE?

38:26.417 --> 38:29.625
