38:51.792 --> 38:53.458
HAPPINESS,
IT FREAKS ME OUT.

38:53.458 --> 38:55.792
IT'S LIKE
ALL THOSE PERFECTLY
MANICURED LAWNS

38:55.792 --> 38:58.166
AT THE BEGINNING
OF BLUE VELVET,
YOU KNOW?

38:58.166 --> 38:59.500
