DON'T YOU, AUDREY?

39:04.834 --> 39:06.417
NO, PLEASE ENLIGHTEN ME.

39:06.417 --> 39:08.417
YOU ARE MUCH MORE AFRAID
TO HAVE SEX WITH ME
THE SECOND TIME

39:08.417 --> 39:09.708
THAN YOU WERE
THE FIRST.

39:09.708 --> 39:12.708
YOU SEE, I'VE HAD A VERY
EDUCATIONAL NIGHT TONIGHT

39:12.708 --> 39:13.708
AT MY FAVORITE GAY BAR,

39:13.708 --> 39:14.917
AND WHAT I'VE COME UP WITH

39:14.917 --> 39:17.166
IS I'M JUST SIMPLY NOT GONNA
TAKE NO FOR AN ANSWER.

39:17.166 --> 39:18.583
WELL, THAT'S NOT
VERY PC OF YOU.

39:18.583 --> 39:22.291
NO, IT'S NOT, AND THIS
PROBABLY ISN'T, EITHER.

39:24.333 --> 39:24.500
MMM.

39:31.542 --> 39:34.166
