[SIGHS]

40:02.708 --> 40:04.458
MMM.

40:07.375 --> 40:10.250
SO HOW'S JOEY?

40:10.250 --> 40:11.708
WOULD YOU BELIEVE
SHE ALMOST HAD AN AFFAIR

40:11.708 --> 40:14.125
WITH HER
