40:14.125 --> 40:15.125
JOEY?

40:15.125 --> 40:16.166
MM-HMM.

40:16.166 --> 40:17.542
JOEY POTTER?

40:17.542 --> 40:19.458
YEAH.

40:19.458 --> 40:20.417
WOW.

40:20.417 --> 40:21.417
IT WAS BIZARRE,
ACTUALLY.

40:21.417 --> 40:24.083
IT WAS, LIKE,
ALMOST LIKE MEETING

40:24.083 --> 40:26.083
