OR SOMETHING.

40:26.083 --> 40:28.708
WHAT DOES THAT MEAN?

40:28.708 --> 40:30.625
I DON'T KNOW.
I JUST...

40:30.625 --> 40:31.750
WELL, LIKE, TALKING
TO HER TONIGHT,

40:31.750 --> 40:35.625
