41:00.792 --> 41:04.667
NO. NOT AS LONG
AS THEY'RE PASSIONATE
ABOUT EACH OTHER.

41:07.625 --> 41:08.667
AND WE ARE.

41:08.667 --> 41:13.000
RIGHT? WE'RE PASSIONATE
ABOUT EACH OTHER.

41:13.000 --> 41:15.208
YOU'RE NOT HAVING DOUBTS
ABOUT US, ARE YOU?

41:15.208 --> 41:20.625
NO. NO, I'M JUST TIRED.

41:20.625 --> 41:23.583
